{
  "info": {
    "name": "University HRMS — Complete API Collection",
    "_postman_id": "hrms-thesis-2025",
    "description": "Complete Postman collection for the University HR Management System.\n\nSETUP:\n1. Set {{baseUrl}} = http://localhost:3000/api/v1\n2. Run 'Login' request first — token is saved automatically to {{token}}\n3. All subsequent requests use Bearer {{token}} automatically\n\nMODULES COVERED:\n- Auth (Login, Refresh, Me, Change Password)\n- Employee Profile (CRUD, Change Requests, Org Chart, Salary, Audit)\n- Time & Attendance (Clock In/Out, Dashboard, Corrections, Overtime, Shifts, Summary)\n- Leave Management (Types, Policies, Balances, Submit/Approve/Cancel Requests, Holidays)\n- Payroll (Config, Runs, Process, Approve, Finalize, Payslips, Exceptions, Bank Files)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000/api/v1" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "employeeId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "attendanceId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "leaveRequestId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "payrollRunId", "value": "1" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "var json = pm.response.json();",
            "if (json.success && json.data.accessToken) {",
            "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.accessToken);",
            "  pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', json.data.refreshToken);",
            "  console.log('Token saved for: ' + json.data.employee.name + ' [' + json.data.employee.role + ']');",
            "}",
            "pm.test('Login successful', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
            "pm.test('Has access token', () => pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('accessToken'));"
          ], "type": "text/javascript" }}],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST", "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth","login"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"sarah.johnson@university.edu\",\n  \"password\": \"HRMSPass123!\"\n}" }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login — FAIL: Wrong Password",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "pm.test('Returns 401', () => pm.response.to.have.status(401));",
            "pm.test('Error code INVALID_CREDENTIALS', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().error.code).to.eql('INVALID_CREDENTIALS'));"
          ], "type": "text/javascript" }}],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST", "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth","login"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"sarah.johnson@university.edu\",\n  \"password\": \"WrongPassword!\"\n}" }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Current User (me)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/me", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth","me"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "var json = pm.response.json();",
            "if (json.success) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.accessToken);",
            "pm.test('Token refreshed', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
          ], "type": "text/javascript" }}],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST", "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth","refresh"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}" }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Change Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }, { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/change-password", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth","change-password"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"currentPassword\": \"HRMSPass123!\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"NewSecure456!\"\n}" }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
